It may seem surreal, but several Muslim bloggers have written letters to Jesus
Christ in their blogs complaining about Western insults against Muslims, and
particularly Dutch MP [Geert
Wilders](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geert_Wilders)‘ anti-Islamic film,
[Fitna](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fitna_\(film\)). Meanwhile, young
Islamist [ Basij](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Basij) paramilitaries
demonstrated in front of the Netherlands embassy in Tehran condemning Wilders’
film.

